text: Elwill M. Shanahan (September 22, 1912 – October 5, 1983) was an American politician who served as the Secretary of State of Kansas from 1966 to 1978. She died of cancer on October 5, 1983, in Topeka, Kansas at age 71. ==References== Category:1912 births Category:1983 deaths Category:Secretaries of State of Kansas Category:Kansas Republicans
title: Elwill M. Shanahan
